{"prompt": "Generate a sleek website for a high-tech manufacturing company. The brand color should be a cool steel blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Advanced Manufacturing Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4682b4; /* Steel Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #a0c2d4; /* Lighter Steel Blue */\n            --background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Very Light Gray */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --heading-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n        }\n        .service-item, .feature-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover, .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-icon, .feature-icon {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-right: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .service-content h3, .feature-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            .service-item, .feature-item {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .service-icon, .feature-icon {\n                margin-right: 0;\n                margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>QuantumForge Industries</h1>\n        <p>Innovating the Future of High-Tech Manufacturing</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Expertise</h2>\n            <p>At QuantumForge Industries, we specialize in pushing the boundaries of what's possible in advanced manufacturing. We leverage cutting-edge technology and precision engineering to deliver unparalleled solutions.</p>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <div class=\"service-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M3 3l3 3m0 0L3 9M6 6l3-3m0 0 3 3M9 3v9M12 3h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3m0 0-3 3m0 0-3-3m6 6L3 21m0 0 3-3m0 0 3 3M9 18v-9M6 21H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3m0 0 3-3m0 0 3 3\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Precision Machining</h3>\n                    <p>Utilizing state-of-the-art CNC machinery and advanced CAM software for unparalleled accuracy and efficiency.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <div class=\"service-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 2L7 7l5 5 5-5-5-5zM6 17l6 5 6-5m0 0-6-5-6 5m6 5v-7m0 0-3-3m3-3 3 3\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>3D Printing & Additive Manufacturing</h3>\n                    <p>Rapid prototyping and production of complex geometries with diverse material capabilities.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <div class=\"service-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M10 20l-5-5 5-5 5 5-5 5zM4 12l6-6 6 6-6 6-6-6zM16 12l6-6 6 6-6 6-6-6z\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Material Science</h3>\n                    <p>Expertise in advanced alloys, composites, and polymers to meet extreme performance demands.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M9 18l6-6-6-6\"/><path d=\"M4 20v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-content\">\n                    <h3>Innovation</h3>\n                    <p>We continuously invest in R&D to stay at the forefront of manufacturing technology.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 17l-6 6-6-6 6-6 6 6z\"/><path d=\"M12 17l6-6 6 6-6 6-6-6z\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-content\">\n                    <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>\n                    <p>Rigorous quality control at every stage ensures products meet the highest standards.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M16 21v-7m-4-5H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v5.5a2 2 0 0 0 2 2.5h5.5a2 2 0 0 1 1.5 2.5v5.5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1.5a2 2 0 0 1 1.5-2.5h3.5a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3.5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3.5a2 2 0 0 1-1.5-2.5v-3.5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2H16\"/></svg>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-content\">\n                    <h3>Scalability</h3>\n                    <p>From rapid prototyping to mass production, we scale to meet your project needs.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <button class=\"cta-button\">Get a Custom Quote</button>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 QuantumForge Industries. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelector('.cta-button').addEventListener('click', () => {\n            alert('Thank you for your interest! Please contact us directly for a custom quote.');\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}